Step_1-basic_setting

Basic Setting for graphql in asp.netcore using hotchocolate server

there are three important dependencies :
1. HotChocolate
2. HotChocolate.AspNetCore
3. HotChocolate.AspNetCore.Playground

In Startup.cs :
1. ConfigureServices: - SchemaBuilder
2. Configure : - app.UseGraphql
               - app.UsePlayground 